items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Soft and cozy

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Comfy sweater
items.body: I love the color of this sweater - wore to church with some lighter color jeans and it was perfect. It is oversized - I normally wear an XS and got this in a small. I don’t feel like I was swimming in it. The sweater is VERY comfortable and I am glad I got this in multiple colors! I am a cold natured person and this sweater kept me warm all day. Great quality! items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Soft and Compliment Magnet
items.body: Sooo soft and I’ve gotten multiple compliments on it every time I wear it. I personally sized up for an oversized look which I prefer, but I think it looks cute either way. Read more

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars A staple in my fall wardrobe
items.body: The sweater is true to size and so very soft! The color wasn’t as vibrant as I had hoped. It is a medium thickness material. Very pretty overall and a staple for my fall wardrobe! Read more
items.author: Liz

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Amazing quality!
items.body: The quality is wonderful! Just bought as a gift. Color is exactly as pictured and size seems to be accurate as well. Read more
items.author: Kelsey Coleman

items.title: 3.0 out of 5 stars This sweater is neither thick nor chunky
items.body: This sweater is neither thick nor chunky... It is in fact thin with a tight knit. I do not think the listing photos or description accurately reflect this sweater at all. The medium did fit loosely but didn't really give that intentional oversized fit...it just kinda felt like I was wearing something too big for me and I didn't think it was at all flattering...felt like it just made me look big as well. I am 5'3", 145lbs with a 36DDD chest and I ordered my normal size medium. The sweater is really soft, but in a silky way. So again, just not what I was expecting based on the model photos. Those to me make the sweater look like it has a more plush texture. The sweater does seem to be well made. The instructions say to hand wash but I don't have the patience for that so I threw in in the machine on cold and hung it to dry. It maintained its shape and didn't start pilling so there's one positive. Ultimately I would say there's nothing significantly wrong with the sweater. But it seriously frustrates me when the photos and descriptions aren't accurate representations of the actual product and thus my star rating. Read more
items.author: Brandi Rede

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars LOVE
items.body: this is my go to sweater now! if it perfectly oversized and not too heavy, so you can still layer it for colder days Read more
items.author: Katharine Y

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Exactly as described
items.body: Exactly as pictured and described. Medium weight thickness with an oversized fit. Super soft with a slight sheen. Read more

short_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

For the best look, smooth the fabric, check the neckline placement, and pair it with shoes that match the occasion and the hem length.

Comfort comes from both the cut and the fabric, so selecting your preferred fit makes a noticeable difference over a full day of wear.

long_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: XS, S, M, L, XL.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: Brown, Blue, Burgundy, Apricot, Army Green, Black, Navy Blue, Dark Brown, Dark Green, Light Blue, Red, Khaki, White, Beige. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
